<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Study Complete</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="debrief-page">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Thank you for participating!</h1>
      <p style="margin:12px 0 20px; color:#4b5563;">Your responses have been recorded. Here is some information about this study.</p>

      <div style="background:#f9fafb; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px; padding:20px; margin-bottom:20px;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:8px;">About this study</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#4b5563; margin-bottom:10px;">
          This study investigated how awareness of AI errors ("hallucinations") affects decision-making vigilance and metacognition.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#4b5563; margin-bottom:10px;">
          The AI assistant you worked with sometimes provided information that did not match the actual data table. This was intentional — we wanted to study whether and how people detect these discrepancies.
        </p>

        <% if (condition === 'experience') { %>
          <p style="font-size:14px; color:#4b5563;">
            <strong>Your condition:</strong> Before the main tasks, you were shown that the AI can make errors (in the practice trial). We are studying whether this early experience makes people more vigilant in subsequent tasks.
          </p>
        <% } else { %>
          <p style="font-size:14px; color:#4b5563;">
            <strong>Your condition:</strong> You were not shown any AI errors before the main tasks. We are comparing your responses to participants who were shown AI errors early on.
          </p>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size:13px; color:#6b7280; margin-bottom:20px;">
        If you have questions about this study, please contact the research team. Your data remains anonymous.
      </p>

      <% if (prolificUrl) { %>
        <a href="<%= prolificUrl %>" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
          Complete on Prolific
        </a>
      <% } else { %>
        <p style="text-align:center; font-size:15px; font-weight:500; color:#16a34a;">
          You may now close this window.
        </p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
